{"tid":933821,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底愛係咩？","createTime":"2018-12-08T18:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T02:30:20.000Z","uid":135359,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"46f6c47d0398a8671eb7e2a8cced7f17b09aac4e","tid":933821,"uid":135359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:29:55.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊兩年幾...<br />\n我係學生 20歲 <br />\n男朋友大我十一年 佢做緊餐飲<br />\n經常ot 一星期最多見到一日全日<br />\n一直疑惑緊 到底仲應唔應該堅持一齊<br />\n因為佢負債差唔多三十萬<br />\n每個月都超過一半人工拎左去還債<br />\n所以平時都唔會太大消費 同埋會aa<br />\n而且我又覺得佢唔係好錫我...<br />\n拗交好多時 都互不相讓<br />\n即使見到我喊晒 佢態度依舊強硬<br />\n朋友話 愛你既男人 見到你喊 點都會低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有時真係好辛苦 唔知為咩⋯<br />\n為左見多d <br />\n佢收夜晚9點 買定佢鐘意既烏龍茶接佢收工<br />\n天氣凍<br />\n買好保暖既衫、睡衣比佢<br />\n而佢呢...好少做呢d<br />\n見住朋友既男朋友咁錫對方<br />\n好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次都想狠心走 但又唔忍心...<br />\n係咪如果愛一個人既話<br />\n應該用青春陪佢捱完還債？"},{"pid":"2756fdde112a8c9ef6cdfded307357a5ce47acbc","tid":933821,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:31:15.000Z","msg":"佢有咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8b099e3fe7d1d4d68aa461962392df9a0c5b58","tid":933821,"uid":135359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2756fdde112a8c9ef6cdfded307357a5ce47acbc","tid":933821,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:31:15.000Z","msg":"佢有咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:34:06.000Z","msg":"嗯..相處好舒服 